title: Double Trouble 2022: Bengals & Steelers
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp tackle one last Double Trouble on the Bengals and Steelers, including if Tee Higgins should be drafted as a WR1 and if Najee Harris is in the elite RB tier. Then, the crew breaks down some of your drafts.
